divs: Sighting Detailsi was at work i work at a gated community in fort myers florida for a tree serive i was going around the left side of the neighbors house and i looked up and i saw what at first i thaught was an airplane intill i relized it didnt make any sound or have any wings..it was cigar shaped and a pale white with what seemed to be black windows on the right side of the craft..it was fairly low to the groun few thousdan feet maybe and flew slow, slower than an airplane landing...i looked off to my right to see an airplane comming in and i looked back at the craft and as i did it vanished and my boss walks over and i just look at him then the sky and spoke jibberish lol and then he said what did u see a ufo? lol yep i did...3 days b4 i saw a tear drop shaped silver craft also so i thaught it was the coolest thing in the world and that noone would believe me but id love to see it again and closer
Summary: whiteish color with what looked like black windows
